Module contents

This package offers machine learning models.

Modules: - REGRESSION_MODELS: Implements regression models. - CLASSIFICATION_MODELS: Implements classification models .

These modules can be imported for building, training and using.

autoop.core.ml.model.get_model(model_name: str) → Model[source]

Factory function to get a model by name.

Args:

model_name (str): Name of the model to retrieve.

Returns:

Model: An instance of the requested model.

Raises:

ValueError: If the model_name is not found in either REGRESSION_MODELS or CLASSIFICATION_MODELS.
